OL,3,CForty firefighters battle large
OL,4,Cheathland wildfire
OL,6,FAround forty firefighters are tackling
OL,7,Fa blaze which has burned through three
OL,8,Fhectares of grass, gorse and
OL,9,Fsurrounding heathland in Fleet.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to a
OL,12,Fthe fire in open land near Norris Hill
OL,13,FRoad, close to the canal, at 10:20am
OL,14,Fon Wednesday 6th May.
OL,16,FMore than 40 firefighters from
OL,17,FRushmoor, Portchester, Fleet,
OL,18,FBasingstoke, Odiham, and Alton remain
OL,19,Fat the scene, supported by Surrey Fire
OL,20,F& Rescue Service.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
