OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778094687
OL,3,CForty firefighters battle large
OL,4,Cheathland wildfire
OL,6,FCrews have been working to bring the
OL,7,Fflames under control, using multiple
OL,8,Fwater jets, hose reels and beaters.
OL,10,FThey took five hours to surround the
OL,11,Ffire, with relief crews remaining in
OL,12,Fattendance on Wednesday evening to
OL,13,Fcontinue damping down hot spots and
OL,14,Fensure the fire is fully extinguished.
OL,16,FNorris Hill Road remains closed to
OL,17,Fallow access for emergency service
OL,18,Fvehicles and members of the public are
OL,19,Furged to avoid the area while
OL,20,Foperations are ongoing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
