OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778094687
OL,3,CForty firefighters battle large
OL,4,Cheathland wildfire
OL,6,FImages from the scene show the
OL,7,Fscorched grassland and areas of gorse,
OL,8,Fhighlighting the damage caused across
OL,9,Fthe heathland.
OL,11,FHampshire & Isle of Wight Fire &
OL,12,FRescue Services said: "This incident
OL,13,Fis an important reminder to always
OL,14,Ftake extra care when visiting open
OL,15,Fcountryside, particularly during dry
OL,16,Fconditions when vegetation can ignite
OL,17,Feasily and fire can spread rapidly."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
